title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show DEC-31-2013 TUES
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show DEC-31-2013 TUES.................PODCAST





The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET

        
      
      The Glenn  Beck Program - 12/31/13Tuesday, December 31, 2013 11:33 AM


The final Glenn Beck Program of 2013 
     and Chris Salcedo is in for Glenn one more time.

  On the agenda is Beyonce's total lack of respect
     for the families of the Challenger tragedy of 1986.

  Also, Beverly Flaxington joins the program to discuss her new book,
        Self-Talk for a Calmer You,
          that discusses the difficulty to find success in business
            during Obama's tenure as president.

  Plus, the lack of respect and following of the American Constitution
                 and Bill of Rights by our government.
